// pages/Support.js
import React from 'react';
import { Box, Heading, Text, Button, Input, FormControl, FormLabel, FormHelperText } from '@chakra-ui/react';

function Support() {
  return (
    <Box>
    <Box textAlign="center" maxWidth="500px" m="auto" bgColor="gray.600" p={10}>
      <Heading>Support Quaapay</Heading>
      <Text mt={3}>Support quaapay company to create more massive features you will enjoy later on.</Text>

      <Button variant="outline" colorScheme="blue" mt={5} mr={2}>
        Give Once
      </Button>
      <Button variant="outline" colorScheme="green" mt={5} ml={2}>
       Give Monthly
      </Button>

      <form>
        <FormControl mt={8}>
          <FormLabel>Name</FormLabel>
          <Input type="text" />
        </FormControl>

        <FormControl mt={4}>
          <FormLabel>Email</FormLabel>
          <Input type="email" />
        </FormControl>

        <FormControl mt={4}>
          <FormLabel>Message</FormLabel>
          <Input type="textarea" />
          <FormHelperText>We'll get back to you as soon as possible.</FormHelperText>
        </FormControl>

        <Button type="submit" colorScheme="blue" mt={6}>
          Submit
        </Button>
      </form>
    </Box>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default Support;
